<h2 class="bold font-l">2003's Astro Boy English Intro</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Instead of True Blue by ZONE in the first episodes and Now or Never in the later ones, the english Dub of the 2003 version of Astro Boy used only this opening for all the episodes. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AlternativeForeignThemeSong" class='trope-example-link'>Alternative Foreign Theme Song</a></p>
