<div id="_pm_videoViewer" class="full-screen">
<a href="#close" class="close" id="_pm_videoViewer-close"></a>
<div class="_pmvv-body">
<div class="_pmvv-vidbox">
<video id='overlay-video-player-box' data-video-id="a773jk" class='video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-16-9'>
</video>
<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">2003's Astro Boy English Intro</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Instead of True Blue by ZONE in the first episodes and Now or Never in the later ones, the english Dub of the 2003 version of Astro Boy used only this opening for all the episodes.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="a773jk">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
<p>How well does it match the trope?</p>
<div id="star-rating-group">
<div class="trope-rate">
<input type="radio" id="lamp5" name="rate" value="5" />
